@node "file" "Pull down menus"

  @{b}Clear@{ub}

  @{b}New@{ub}           -   Amiga + n
(see @{"GUI description" link "other"})

  @{b}Open@{ub}          -   Amiga + o

  @{b}Save@{ub}          -   Amiga + w

  @{b}Save As@{ub}       -   Amiga + W

  @{b}About a file@{ub}  -   Amiga + ?

  @{b}About@{ub}

  @{b}Iconify@{ub}       -   Amiga + i

  @{b}Quit@{ub}          -   Amiga + q

@endnode

@node "move" "Pull down menus"

 @{b}Beg of file@{ub}          -    Control + (up arrow)

 @{b}End of file@{ub}          -    Control + (down arrow)

 @{b}Prev page@{ub}            -    Shift + (up arrow)

 @{b}Next page     @{ub}       -    Shift + (down arrow)

 @{b}Jump to line   @{ub}      -    Amiga + j

 @{b}Jump to byte  @{ub}       -    Amiga + J

@endnode

@node "search" "Pull down menus"

@{b}Repeat search forwards@{ub}          -  Amiga + s

@{b}Repeat search backwards@{ub}         -  Amiga + a

@{b}Search for letters@{ub}              -  Amiga + d
Searching for letters ("A" to "Z" i "a" to "z").

@{b}Search for words@{ub}              -  Amiga + f
Searching for "words".
ex. of "words": abssdd, aaaaa, ble - (min. 3xletter)

@{b}Minimum size of word@{ub}
You can change minimum size of "word".


@{b}Clip (ANSI)/(HEX) to search/replace bufer@{ub}
Moves clip to search or replace buffer (ANSI or HEX).


@{b}Repeat replace@{ub}                  -  Amiga + r

@{b}Replace...  @{ub}                     -  Amiga + R
It replaces given value with other.
The same window as in Search (see below).

@{b}Count...  @{ub}                       -  Amiga + g
It counts occurrences of given value in file.
The same window as in Search (see below).


@{b}Search for...  @{ub}                     -  Amiga + S
Search window:

@{b} - checkbox Letters.@{ub}
  Like above. You can use it with checkbox Numbers.

@{b} -  Numbers.@{ub}
  Searching for numbers...

@{b} -  Words.@{ub}
  Searching for words... It turn off Letters & Numbers.

@{b} - Forward.@{ub}
  Like in cED.

@{b} - Ignore case.@{ub}
ex.  "A"="a".

@{b} - Search in hex mode. @{ub}
Searching for hex values.

@{b} - Start at top.@{ub}
  savED will start searching from the beginning of file (if Forward is checked) or from
the end of file.

@{b} - Replace in hex mode. @{ub}
Replaces with hex values.

@{b} - Align to end.@{ub}
ex.

  Locate:   FFFFFFFF
  Replace:  A

If ON:
  FFFFFFFF
     |
     V
  0000000A

If OFF:
  FFFFFFFF
     |
     V
  A0000000
(in examaple "clear if smaller" is ON)


@{b} - Clear if smaller.@{ub}
ex.

  Locate:   FFFFFFFF
  Replace:  A

If ON:
  FFFFFFFF
     |
     V
  A0000000  -  savED clear unused bytes

If OFF:
  FFFFFFFF
     |
     V
  AFFFFFFF
(in this example "Align to end" is OFF)

@{b} - Cut if bigger.@{ub}
ex.

  Locate:   abcdefg
  Replace:  bbbbbbbbbbb

If ON:
  abcdefgijklmn
     |
     V
  @{b}bbbbbbb@{ub}ijklmn

If OFF:
  abcdefgijklmn
     |
     V
  @{b}bbbbbbbbbbb@{ub}mn
(in example "Align to end" is OFF)

@endnode
@node "edit" "Pull down menus"

@{b} Mark @{ub}                   -  Amiga + b
You can mark area, by moving cursor.


@{b} copy @{ub}                   -  Amiga + c
It copies marked area to clip.

@{b} cut @{ub}                   -  Amiga + x
It copies marked area to clip and fill markes area with zeroa.

@{b} Paste @{ub}                   -  Amiga + v
It copies clip to main window.

@{b} Undo @{ub}                   -  Amiga + u

@{b} Redo   @{ub}                 -  Amiga + U

@{b} Max undo levels@{ub}

@{b} Edit in hex@{ub}
Change edit mode to hex.

@{b} Edit in ASCII@{ub}
Change edit mode to ASCII.

@endnode
@node "other" "Pull down menus"

@{b}Calc @{ub}                          -  Amiga + k
This window doesn't freeze main window.

Gadgets:
 - two string gadgets @{b}Dec and Hex@{ub}. They are translators between hex and dec.

 - button @{b}Search@{ub}.  It opens search window and moves value from string gadget
in calc window to search window.

 - przycisku @{b}Jump@{ub}.  Like above, but this opens jump window.

 - przycisku @{b}Insert@{ub}. It insert value from calc to main window.

Those three buttons are briges between calc, search, jump and main window.

@{b}
WARNING:  Those three buttons (Search, Jump, Insert) are disabled 
          in demo version
.@{ub}
 - @{b}Exit@{ub}



@{b}change size od file@{ub}
Gadgets:
 o two integer gadgets @{b}Beg and End of file@{ub} with buttons. Buttons "<" and ">"
    have shortcuts: "[" and "]"  moves beginning, "{" and "}" moves end.
 o @{b}Size of file@{ub}. 


@endnode
