@node "rejestracja" "How to register?"

The registration fee is 10 PLN (or 10 DM (mark), $10 (dollar), Ł10 (pound)). 

You can choose between various methods of payment:

 - Send money in an envelope, together with the registration form

 - Make an international postal money order, and send the registration
   form in an envelope (or e-mail).

 - Make a bank draft, and send it in the envelope together with the
   registration form (please, first verify that your bank draft can
   be cashed in Poland)

 First, I suggest to contact with me via e-mail.

You can choose whether to receive registed savED via e-mail or via normal mail.

 - If you decide to receive it via e-mail, please specify your e-mail address
   on the registration form.

 - If you decide to receive it via normal mail, please enclose a pre-formatted
   floppy disk (DD or HD) into the envelope (or 5 PLN (or 3 DM/$2/Ł2) and I will
   defray cost of floppy disk and shipment).


Please print and fill in the registration form and send it:
 - in envolope together with payment.
 - or via e-mail.


